# Canon-rule inbox

Capture step of the plan-to-canon process. Drop a markdown file here
whenever a voice pattern gets flagged in a draft, review, or
conversation. Filename: YYYY-MM-DD-short-slug.md.

Once a pattern appears here three times (across same or different
authors), promote it to canon per Step 2 of the lifecycle in
docs/canon-revisions/2026-05-19-plan-to-canon-process.md.

Use the template in §"Capture template" of that doc.
